comment_data.body:
Maybe only display this on Android?
```
import 'dart:io';

...

Platorm.isAndroid
  ? ListTile(...)
  : SizedBox.shrink()
```

Could also be moved into a _maybeBuildQuitButton helper if inline-conditionals seem messy.

comment_data.body: This undoes the formatting Android Studio automatically gives the imports, and https://dart.dev/guides/language/effective-dart/style#ordering seems to agree that the AS formatting is blessed. Strange that the fmt check doesn't catch that.
Maybe it's a separate lint check that we must enable: https://dart.dev/tools/linter-rules#directives_ordering
